{"questionId":"3131288","questionHtml":"<p>Determine an expression for the derivative <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>T</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>attempt at chain rule&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>T</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>15</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mi>x</mi><msqrt><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><msup><mn>4</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><msqrt><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><msup><mn>8</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for each correct term. Accept any equivalent form i.e. condone fractions not simplified.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3131288","referenceCode":"23M.3.AHL.TZ2.1ci","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Determine an expression for the derivative T'(x).","paper":"3","level":"HL","questionNumber":"i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 5—Calculus","Topic 5—Calculus","AHL 5.9—Differentiating standard functions and derivative rules"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}